item.title: CVE-2023-27268|2024-08-02T12:09:41.865Z -- sap -- netweaver%20as%20java%20%28object%20analyzing%20service%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS Java (Object Analyzing Service) - version 7.50, does not perform necessary authorization checks, allowing an unauthenticated attacker to attach to an open interface and make use of an open naming and directory API to access a service which will enable them to access but not modify server settings and data with no effect on availability., resulting in escalation of privileges.
